  "title": "In-House Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<ul><li>To assist in conceptualizing, visualizing, and executing creative graphic artwork for marketing and communication-related items.</li><li>To assist in creating social media community content to increase engagement and improve overall brand presence on social media.</li><li>Work with in-house Copywriter, Marketer to increase overall campaign performance on Facebook, Facebook Ads, Instagram, Tiktok & Google Ads.</li><li>Work closely with the E-commerce team to assist in developing marketing content for upcoming sales events and promotions.</li><li>Assist in product shoots.</li><li>Based on the company's promotion campaign assist to design marketing content.</li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>Liaise with departments to understand their technical requirements.</li><li>At least Diploma/Degree in Creative/Graphic Design/Visual or related fields.</li><li>Experienced with Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop. Premiere Pro, After Effects (Preferably)</li><li>Demonstrable graphic design skills with a decent portfolio.</li><li>Innovative, diligent, analytical and possesses good problem-solving skills.</li><li>Knowledge of photography skill will be an advantage.</li><li>Knowledge of \"Adobe PR, AE\" with simple video editing will be an added advantage.</li></ul>",
