    "description": "<p>TOYOGO is a Singaporean homegrown brand that has proudly manufactured and sold high-quality, sustainable plastic products for over 40 years. Specializing in a diverse range of household and industrial plastic products, including storage boxes, drawers, chairs, stools, containers, crates, pallets, and racks, we have gained the trust of countless Singaporean and Malaysian families and businesses. Our commitment to excellence, affordability, and customer satisfaction remains at the core of everything we do.<br /><br />At TOYOGO, we are committed to providing a supportive and inclusive work environment where our employees can thrive. We offer a range of benefits including competitive remuneration, opportunities for career development, and a collaborative team culture. As we continue to grow, we are always on the lookout for talented individuals to join our dynamic team.</p>",
